Job description
Let’s become our Junior/Mid QA Engineer, and you will
Develop different technology projects of 7-Eleven VN;
Work closely with product managers and business stakeholders, analyze the requirements and feedback to improve the requirement itself;
Participate in all stages of agile product development life cycle with Scrum.
 We expect you to
Design, implement and update test cases for the 7-Eleven Viet Nam Retail System. E.g: the Store Computer, 7-Eleven app;
Responsible for writing a test plan, performing tests to ensure the quality of each release;
Investigate, troubleshoot, and document test failures of communication to the development team;
Managing the cycle of arising and ending of defects/bugs;
Prepare reports to communicate the outcomes of quality activities;
Join the process of writing user guide/user support and every time develop a new function;
Responsible for providing support, finding the root cause in case the end-user faces system errors.

requirement:
Your skills and experience

1-3 years of experience in testing;
Strong skills in manual testing for Web/Mobile/API;
Experience in developing test cases, executing tests and reporting test results;
Experience in working with database, and SQL queries;
Experience in performance, security testing;
Skills in problem solving, judgment, critical thinking and decision making;
Execute and manage resources for testing activities in different agile teams;
Review requirements and technical documents to provide timeline feedback;
Good communication skills and an eager-to-learn mindset.
